  <brief_title>Effect of Traditional Chinese Medicine on GI Function Recovery and Nutrition Support in SAP</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Traditional Chinese Medicine on Gastrointestinal Function Recovery and Nutrition Support in Severe Acute Pancreatitis</official_title>
