  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      With multicenter randomized control clinical evaluation investigations, the effect of
      traditional Chinese medicine on gastrointestinal function recovery and nutrition support in
      early stage of severe acute pancreatitis (SAP) was evaluated, and the therapeutic effects,
      safety and indications assured. Drawing in latest research fruits at home and abroad, a
      clinical practical guideline would be formed, to be popularized all over China.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
